<varlistentry>
<term><menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu>
<guimenuitem>Configure</guimenuitem> </menuchoice></term>
<listitem><para><action>Lets you configure the File manager, File Associations,
Browser, Internet Keywords, Cookies, Proxies, Key Bindings or Toolbars by
bringing up the appropriate dialog box</action></para></listitem>
</varlistentry>

</variablelist>

